                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8055" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1242</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1983 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“中国奶茶第一股”香飘飘怎么不香了？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;The first share of Chinese milk tea&quot; Why doesn&#39;t Xiang Piao Piao smell?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵青华，冯柯柯，蔡锦楠，官钰芹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">香飘飘食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">香飘飘；品牌老化；奶茶；品牌活化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Xiang Piao Piao; Brand aging; Tea with milk; Brand activation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20世纪以来，随着居民消费水平日益增强，奶茶开始受到广大年轻消费者的喜爱，香飘飘另辟蹊径推出方便、便宜的杯装奶茶，搭上了奶茶市场的春风成为奶茶王者，但随着消费者健康意识的提高以及新式茶饮的崛起，香飘飘冲泡奶茶优势正在逐渐弱化。本案例以“奶茶王者”香飘飘为研究对象，介绍了香飘飘缔造杯装奶茶神话的发展历程，描述了其在面对争先恐后的竞争者时采取的品牌管理策略，及其在市场环境快速更迭和新式茶饮的冲击下王者势微的过程。案例旨在引导学生理解品牌管理策略对企业发展的重要性，分析香飘飘品牌老化的表现及原因，了解品牌年轻化的必要性，启发学生思考和探索香飘飘的品牌活化措施，并为面临品牌老化困境的相关企业提供有益启示与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the 20th century, with the increasing consumption level of residents, milk tea has begun to be loved by the majority of young consumers. Xiangpiaopiao created a new way to introduce convenient and cheap cup milk tea, and became the king of milk tea with the spring breeze of the milk tea market. However, with the improvement of consumers&#39; health awareness and the rise of new tea drinks, the advantage of Xiangpiaopiao brewing milk tea is gradually weakening. This case takes Xiangpiaopiao, the &quot;king of milk tea&quot;, as the research object, introduces the development process of Xiangpiaopiao creating the myth of cup packed milk tea, describes its marketing strategy in the face of competing competitors, and the process of the king&#39;s decline under the impact of rapid changes in the market environment and new tea drinks. The case aims to guide students to understand the importance of brand management strategy for enterprise development, analyze the performance and causes of Xiangpiaopiao brand aging, understand the necessity of brand rejuvenation, inspire students to think about and explore Xiangpiaopiao brand activation measures, and provide useful inspiration and reference for relevant enterprises facing the dilemma of brand aging.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌管理；品牌老化；品牌活化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
